name: Shibasso

He knows that if you believe in yourslef, you can make anything a meme. With help from his frens, Shibasso achieves any goal he sets his mind to. in 2024 shibasso set a new goal, to create the dankest meme the world had ever seen. in 2024, shibasso created $shibasso.
